We can’t let politics get in the way of making it easier for American workers and businesses to prosper through international trade. That’s why it’s time for Congress to ratify USMCA.
USMCA strengthens our relationships and increases American access to Canadian and Mexican markets. It’s a win for US manufacturing, auto industry, and our farmers.

It’s been 25 years since NAFTA, since then our economies have changed. The rise of the internet, tech revolution in manufacturing and ag industries have outpaced it. It’s time for a trade deal that reflects those changes.

When we export American-made products, it benefits American workers. Int’l trade must be done on a level playing field. That’s why it’s important to approve USMCA. https://twitter.com/SteveScalise/status/1138518987275427840 …
